COMMENTS ON ANY OTHER CONDITIONS AFFECTING THIS STREAM
Poor return of chums, but better than the rest of the sub-area - possibly because of consistent water flow. The final number was probably higher than recorded,
but I was unable to get to this system for a final walk at the end of October.
